> + * (C) 2000-2001 by Harald Welte <laforge@gnumonks.org>
>   * based on a copy of RR's ip_nat_ftp.c
>   *
> - * ip_nat_irc.c,v 1.15 2001/10/22 10:43:53 laforge Exp
